            <lg xml:id="TK757">
<l>aruḷeṉṉu maṉpīṉ kuḻavi poruḷeṉṉuñ</l>
<l>celvac ceviliyā luṇṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The child mercy which is borne by love grows under the care of the rich nurse of wealth.</l>
            </lg>
